body.text:
Dear {{user_name}},

Your patent '{{patent_title}}' (ID: {{patent_id}}) has been analyzed by the PatentAnalyzer system.

Alert Type: {{alert_type}}
Risk Level: {{risk_level}}

Analysis Summary:
{{analysis_summary}}

{% if prior_art_matches %}Prior Art Matches:
{% for match in prior_art_matches %}
- {{match.title}} (Similarity: {{match.similarity_score}}%)
  Patent ID: {{match.patent_id}}
  Key Overlap: {{match.key_overlap}}
{% endfor %}{% endif %}

{% if infringement_risks %}Potential Infringement Risks:
{% for risk in infringement_risks %}
- {{risk.title}} (Risk Score: {{risk.risk_score}}%)
  Patent ID: {{risk.patent_id}}
  Critical Factors: {{risk.critical_factors}}
{% endfor %}{% endif %}

To view the complete analysis, please log in to your PatentAnalyzer dashboard:
{{dashboard_url}}

If you have any questions or concerns, please contact our support team.

Best regards,
The PatentAnalyzer Team
